@api
Feature: Get recommended programs

    To find programs with tags and extensions, which are similar to the tags and extensions of one selected program

  Background:
    Given there are extensions:
      | id | name         | prefix    |
      | 1  | Arduino      | ARDUINO   |
      | 2  | Drone        | DRONE     |
      | 3  | Lego         | LEGO      |
      | 4  | Phiro        | PHIRO     |
      | 5  | Raspberry Pi | RASPI     |
    And there are tags:
      | id | en           |
      | 1  | Games        |
      | 2  | Animation    |
      | 3  | Story        |
      | 4  | Music        |
      | 5  | Art          |
      | 6  | Experimental |
    And there are programs:
      | id | name      | description | owned by | downloads | views | upload time      | version | extensions | tags_id |
      | 1  | Game      | p4          | Catrobat | 5         | 1     | 01.03.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   |            | 5       |
      | 2  | Minions   | p1          | Catrobat | 3         | 12    | 01.01.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   | Lego,Phiro | 1,2,3,4 |
      | 3  | Galaxy    | p2          | Catrobat | 10        | 13    | 01.02.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   | Lego,Drone | 1,2,3   |
      | 4  | Alone     | p3          | Catrobat | 5         | 1     | 01.03.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   |            | 1,2     |
      | 5  | Trolol    | p5          | Catrobat | 5         | 1     | 01.03.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   | Lego       | 5       |


  Scenario: A request must have specific parameters to succeed with the recommender api

    Given I have a parameter "program_id" with value "1"
    And I have a parameter "limit" with value "10"
    And I have a parameter "offset" with value "0"
    When I GET "/pocketcode/api/projects/recsys.json" with these parameters
    Then I should get following programs:
      | Name      |
      | Trolol    |


  Scenario: You get recommended programs which are more similar to the selected program first

    Given I use the limit "10"
    And I use the offset "0"
    When I search similar programs for program id "2"
    Then I should get following programs:
      | Name      |
      | Galaxy    |
      | Alone     |
      | Trolol    |
